text: Frankie Stein is a fictional character in the television series Monster High. They are the child of Frankenstein. Frankie is voiced by Kate Higgins. Frankie is 15 days old. They are clumsy, polite, and athletic, but a good friend. Frankie has black and white hair. Their body is made of stitches and bolts. They are the new ghoul at Monster High. Their best ghoul friends are Draculaura and Clawdeen Wolf. When they are nervous their bolts begin to spark and they give people a bit of a shock. Category:Television characters
title: Frankie Stein (Monster High)
